---
// Hero editorial: article vedette + 2 articles secondaires
---

<section class="pt-32 pb-12 relative noise-overlay">
  <!-- Gradient background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-violet-dim/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Category tag -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-gold/10 text-gold border border-gold/20 rounded-full">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-gold animate-pulse-dot"></span>
        A la une
      </span>
      <span class="text-xs text-text-muted">10 Février 2026</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      <!-- Main Featured Article -->
      <article class="lg:col-span-7 group cursor-pointer animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
        <a href="/article/bitcoin-franchit-100k" class="block">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div class="relative aspect-[16/9] rounded-card overflow-hidden mb-6 bg-surface">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/20 via-violet/10 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-void/80 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            <!-- Placeholder visual -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gold/5 border border-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gold/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Reading time badge -->
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium glass rounded-full">
              8 min
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold bg-violet/10 text-violet-light border border-violet/20 rounded-full">Bitcoin</span>
              <span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold bg-surface-raised text-text-secondary rounded-full">Analyse</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="font-display font-800 text-display-lg leading-[1.1] group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200 tracking-tight">
              Bitcoin franchit les 100K$ : l'aube d'un nouveau cycle haussier
            </h1>
            <p class="text-body-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
              Après des mois de consolidation, Bitcoin vient de dépasser la barre symbolique des 100 000 dollars. Analyse des facteurs macro, on-chain et institutionnels qui propulsent cette hausse historique.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-violet flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-void">ML</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium">Marc Lefebvre</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">Analyste Senior</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Side Articles -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6">
        <!-- Side Article 1 -->
        <article class="group cursor-pointer flex gap-5 animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
          <a href="/article/ethereum-etf-explosion" class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="relative w-40 min-w-[10rem] aspect-[4/3] rounded-card overflow-hidden bg-surface flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-info/20 via-violet/10 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-info/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M11.944 17.97L4.58 13.62 11.943 24l7.37-10.38-7.372 4.35h.003zM12.056 0L4.69 12.223l7.365 4.354 7.365-4.35L12.056 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-2 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-info">Ethereum</span>
              <h2 class="font-display font-700 text-h3 leading-snug group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200 line-clamp-3">
                ETF Ethereum : les flux entrants explosent tous les records
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Il y a 3 heures</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <!-- Separator -->
        <div class="border-t border-border"></div>

        <!-- Side Article 2 -->
        <article class="group cursor-pointer flex gap-5 animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
          <a href="/article/defi-renaissance" class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="relative w-40 min-w-[10rem] aspect-[4/3] rounded-card overflow-hidden bg-surface flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-positive/20 via-gold/10 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-positive/30" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.307a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.519l2.74-1.22m0 0l-5.94-2.28m5.94 2.28l-2.28 5.941" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-2 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-positive">DeFi</span>
              <h2 class="font-display font-700 text-h3 leading-snug group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200 line-clamp-3">
                DeFi Renaissance : la TVL dépasse les 200 milliards de dollars
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Il y a 5 heures</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <!-- Separator -->
        <div class="border-t border-border"></div>

        <!-- Side Article 3 -->
        <article class="group cursor-pointer flex gap-5 animate-fade-in-up delay-400">
          <a href="/article/regulation-europe" class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="relative w-40 min-w-[10rem] aspect-[4/3] rounded-card overflow-hidden bg-surface flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/20 via-surface to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-gold/30" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0012 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-2 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gold">Régulation</span>
              <h2 class="font-display font-700 text-h3 leading-snug group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200 line-clamp-3">
                MiCA 2.0 : l'Europe pose les bases de la régulation mondiale
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Il y a 8 heures</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
